    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. <date>Anno tricesimo sexto regnante domino Constantino
                            magno imperatore, et decimo anno principatus domni <persName
                                key="#Princeps" ref="#people/156">Landulfi</persName> gloriosi <rs
                                key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, et anno sexto principatus domni
                                <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/157">Pandulfi</persName>
                            filii eius, mense iulio, septima indiccione</date>. Memoratorium factum
                        a me <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1939">Leone</persName>,<rs
                            key="#Abbots"> abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1900" key="#Monasteries #Abbots">Sancti
                            Vincencii</orgName>, et <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Other_palatine_officer"
                            ref="#people/1944">Adelferi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendario</rs><rs
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"> abbocatore</rs> meo de
                        hoc, quod in sacratissimo <placeName ref="#places/110"
                            key="#Assembly #Palatium">Beneventano</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palacio</rs>, in presencia domni Landulfi
                        excellentissimi principis, ubi coram eo residebat domnus <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#people/1945">Iohannes</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Bishops">pontiphex</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Bishops" ref="#juridical_persons/1913">Sancte Beneventane
                            Sedis</orgName>, atque coram eis <rs key="#Assembly">astante</rs>
                        <persName key="#Judge #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#people/1946"
                            >Raimelfrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldeo</rs> et <rs key="#Judge"
                            >iudice</rs>, per <rs key="#Placitum/iudicatum">iudicium</rs> supradicte
                        potestatis vuadiatus sum cum <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            ref="#people/1947">Alfano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldeo</rs>, pro parte supradicti
                        palacii, et cum <persName
                            key="#Deacons #Abbots #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            ref="#people/1949">Iohanne</persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diacono</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocatore</rs> predicti
                        episcopii, tali tenore, ut ad dies duodecim facerem ego eorum talem
                        consignacionem, iuxta legem, cum tercia persona, ita ut singuli separatim
                        dicant: “Scio quia <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1912">Sancti Salvatoris</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/112">Alife</placeName> liberum fuit factum da episcopo
                        Beneventano, et palacium illum subdidit Sancto Vincencio, ut talem
                        dominacionem haberet ibi, qualem abbas debet habere in monasterio; et postea
                        ipsi cum quinque scariones predicti nostri monasterii firmarent per
                        sacramentum ipsam consignacionem. Unde ipsi a parte sua de taliter
                        recipiendum mediatorem nobis posuerunt <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/1948">Sadipertum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">stolfaiz</rs>, et nos eorum mediatorem
                        posuimus. Hoc breve, ex iussione supradicte potestatis, scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Other_clerics"><name ref="Madelfrit"
                                >Madelfrit</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericus</rs> et <rs key="#Notary"
                        >notarius</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
